high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the salt on the corner of the table the coffee maker is on.
Pick up the salt on the corner of the table.
Turn left and walk forward and look up to face the cabinet above the right side of the microwave.
Place the salt in the cabinet above the left side of the microwave.
Turn around and walk around the white table to face the salt in the center of the table.
Pick up the salt in the center of the white table.
Turn right and walk forward and look up to face the cabinet above the right side of the microwave.
Place the salt in the cabinet above the left side of the microwave next to the first salt.
anns.task_desc: To place two salts in the cabinet above the right side of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the dishwasher to your right.
Pick up the salt on the front, right corner of the dishwasher.
Turn to your left and go to the cabinets above the microwave.
Place the salt in the right cabinet above the microwave.
Turn around and go to the white table on your right.
Pick up the salt in front of the butter knife, on the table.
Turn to your right and go back to the cabinet above the microwave.
Place the salt in the right cabinet above the microwave, to the right of the other sat.
anns.task_desc: Put two items of salt in the cabinet.

high_descs: Walk over to where the coffee machine is on the counter.
Pick up the salt shaker that is on the front left corner of the counter.
Turn left and walk across the room to the microwave, then look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the cabinet door in front of you and put the salt shaker inside, then close the door.
Walk over to the large white table behind you.
Pick up the salt shaker closest to the front edge of the table.
Turn right and walk over to the microwave, then look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the upper cabinet in front of you and put the salt shaker inside, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Move two salt shakers into a cabinet.
